item.title: Baseline
item.description: Baseline tune # There are some fantastic printer tuning guides out there, and I have absolutely no intention of replacing them. In fact, I’ll be linking to a number of them through the tuning guide with the expectation that you’ll use their guides. To start off with, Matt (the creator of THE 100), has a great video on how he tunes 3d printers. Matt starts his video by mentioning Ellis’ Print Tuning Guide which is the most detailed guide I’ve ever used.
